{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"setEmails:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:completion:"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses with completion handler.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"emails","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings."}]}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Same as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setEmails:"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server registration completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use this for confirmation UI or to chain dependent operations.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Import emails from third-party login with confirmation:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class SocialLoginHandler {","","    func handleGoogleSignIn(_ user: GIDGoogleUser) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        \/\/ Primary email from Google","        if let email = user.profile?.email {","            emails.append(email)","        }","","        \/\/ Additional emails from Google profile if available","        if let additionalEmails = user.profile?.additionalEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: additionalEmails)","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Analytics.track(\"email_sync_failed\", properties: [","                    \"provider\": \"google\",","                    \"email_count\": emails.count,","                    \"error\": error.localizedDescription","                ])","                return","            }","","            Analytics.track(\"email_sync_success\", properties: [","                \"provider\": \"google\",","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            \/\/ Set user ID from Google","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.userID ?? \"\")","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:completion:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers multiple email addresses with completion handler."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:completion:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:completion:"}],"title":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:completion:","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"}}}